/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/27\/best-worship-recitation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34671,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: Best worship is recitation of the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best act of worship for my nation is reciting the Quran.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 1865 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Safirini \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064f\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/28\/husn-al-dhann-bi-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34671,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Optimism: Good thoughts about Allah is worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, thinking well about Allah Almighty is a part of the excellent worship of Allah.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8694 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ahmad Shakir. \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u06